snippet.title: AntVentor – official game trailer
snippet.description:
AntVentor is a point & click game about inventor ant and his adventures in the photo-realistic macroworld
www.antventor.com

PLAY AntVentor at your favorite store:
➤ Steam Store (PC/MAC/Linux) 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/739190/AntVentor/
➤ MacAppStore (MAC only)
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/antventor/id1378011538 
➤ AppStore (iPhone/iPad/iPod)
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/antventor/id1405952969
➤ Android (Smartphone/Tablet)
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.LoopyMood.AntVentor
➤ Android TV (NVIDIA SHIELD)
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.LoopyMood.AntVentor.shield
➤ Amazon App Store (Tablets)
https://www.amazon.com/LoopyMood-AntVentor/dp/B07J6MXK73/ 
➤ Humble Bundle (Steam codes)
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/antventor
